  // Source: local quest reference (structure/ordering) cross-referenced with the
  // EFT wiki (objective text + optional/required flags). Chapters are the storyline
  // narrator-trader quests; objectives are the ordered sub-quest references. Optional
  // flags come from the wiki. Chapter ordering, wikiLink, activation, and requirements
  // are curated (scripts/story-chapter-meta.json). Each objective records
  // sourceQuestId/sourceObjectiveId for traceability. The Ticket keeps its curated
  // branching (endings + mutual exclusion). Regenerate with `npm run eft:story`.
  // The storyline is shared between PVP and PVE.
  //
  // Objectives can carry task-style marker data (maps, zones, possibleLocations,
  // requiredKeys, item/items/markerItem/questItem, count, foundInRaid) for map
  // rendering; see docs/MASTER_SAMPLES.md.

